Module org.example.camping2
Package org.example.camping2.dao

Class DAOGN<T,ID>

java.lang.Object
org.example.camping2.dao.DAOGN<T,ID>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of entity the DAO will manage.
ID - The type of the entity's identifier (ID).
public class DAOGN<T,ID> extends Object
Generic DAO (Data Access Object) class that provides common database operations (add, update, delete, find) for any entity type. It uses JPA (Jakarta Persistence API) and an EntityManager to interact with the database.
